{
  "stem": "5471.4",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I thought I have to do something about the girls.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The greengrocer who came in, he was [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I said to him, [NON-ENGLISH], promise me, when they pick us two up, take care that the-- the kids come outside the camp.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he said, I'll build them in between the crates.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So as soon as I hear that you have been taken away, I'll come over and I'll take the girls out.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So that was my biggest or my anxious moments, that they would do something with the girls.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But we stayed there, so.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We have often said, why didn't-- didn't he send you to a concentration camp?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] they had their [NON-ENGLISH] in time.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They had everything they wanted to.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They knew when they sent my husband out who would replace him.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So it was in there, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] it was the best way for them when you stayed in-- in the camp.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And when the-- on the 11th of April, '45, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] we were-- we-- we knew already beforehand that they were losing.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So the end must be near.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my husband had been to Westerbork, township of Westerbork, 8 kilometers from us.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he had made contact with the Canadians and told them what to do when the end was there.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so on the 11th of April I was sitting outside with my parents, beautiful weather.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And came a little girl to me, a [NON-ENGLISH], little girl was helping.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "She said, Mrs. van As, don't be afraid.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Everything will be all right.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
